   <S PAR='28' RSNT='1' SNO='28'>PREFACE</S>
   <S PAR='29' RSNT='1' SNO='29'>This book is composed of messages concerning the organization of the church given by Brother Witness Lee during a training on service in Taipei, Taiwan in 1956.</S>
   <S PAR='30' RSNT='1' SNO='30'>The general subject of the training was Three Aspects of the Church.</S>
   <S PAR='31' RSNT='1' SNO='31'>The first aspect is the meaning of the church; the second, the course of the church; and the third, the organization of the church.</S>
   <S PAR='32' RSNT='1' SNO='32'>The messages given in this training were compiled into three books, according to the three aforementioned aspects; these books are subtitled: The Meaning of the Church, The Course of the Church, and The Organization of the Church.</S>
